import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import {ShoppingCartOutlined} from '@material-ui/icons'

const Product = ({item}) => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Circle />
            <Image src={item.img}/>
            <Info>
                <Icon>
                    <ShoppingCartOutlined />
                </Icon>
            </Info>
        </Container>
    )
}

const Container = styled.div`

`;
export default Product
